data.description: This is a dream home indeed! FOUR FANTASTIC LEVELS! The NEW stainless steel appliances are a sleek addition to that already fabulous kitchen. Picture yourself whipping up delicious meals and serving them on the large Corian countertop. The all-brick exterior with some new windows, solar panels, and courtyard entryway set the stage for a warm welcome, and the connection to a beautiful backyard and open park is simply enchanting. And with the possibility of a fourth bedroom, this home is a rare find indeed. I AM BIGGER THAN I LOOK! Have you had the chance to see it in person yet?
